:name:
Occult

:pool: 
Reason

:p: 
R

:coretxt:
There exist odd things in the world.
Occult is about knowing about those.
It is used to know about mystical things or when researching those.
Usually obtained by witches, inquisitors, and conspiricy theorists.
Skill determines how well you have found out what is actually true and what is not.

